comment: * Columns from the Attendees table that other tables join into themselves.

variables.name: EVENT_ID
variables.comment:
* The id of the event. Column name. *

Type: INTEGER

variables.name: ATTENDEE_NAME
variables.comment:
* The name of the attendee. Column name. *

Type: STRING

variables.name: ATTENDEE_EMAIL
variables.comment:
* The email address of the attendee. Column name. *

Type: STRING

variables.name: ATTENDEE_RELATIONSHIP
variables.comment:
* The relationship of the attendee to the user. Column name. *

Type: INTEGER (one of {@link #RELATIONSHIP_ATTENDEE}, ...}.

variables.name: ATTENDEE_TYPE
variables.comment:
* The type of attendee. Column name. *

* Type: Integer (one of {@link #TYPE_NONE}, {@link #TYPE_REQUIRED}, * {@link #TYPE_OPTIONAL}, {@link #TYPE_RESOURCE}) *

variables.name: TYPE_RESOURCE
variables.comment:
* This specifies that an attendee is a resource, like a room, a
         * cabbage, or something and not an actual person.

variables.name: ATTENDEE_STATUS
variables.comment:
* The attendance status of the attendee. Column name. *

Type: Integer (one of {@link #ATTENDEE_STATUS_ACCEPTED}, ...).

variables.name: ATTENDEE_IDENTITY
variables.comment:
* The identity of the attendee as referenced in * {@link ContactsContract.CommonDataKinds.Identity#IDENTITY}. * This is required only if {@link #ATTENDEE_ID_NAMESPACE} is present. Column name. *

Type: STRING

variables.name: ATTENDEE_ID_NAMESPACE
variables.comment:
* The identity name space of the attendee as referenced in * {@link ContactsContract.CommonDataKinds.Identity#NAMESPACE}. * This is required only if {@link #ATTENDEE_IDENTITY} is present. Column name. *

Type: STRING
